results.name: Fourier coefficients of T_{12}.
comment: T_{12} is a weight = -10 normalized meromorphic modular form for SL(2,Z) with all poles at infinity.
reference: C. L. Siegel, Advanced Analytic Number Theory, Tata Institute of Fundamental Research, Bombay, 1980, pp. 249-268.
